---
title: Beef Meatballs and Mashed Potato with a rich spinach sauce
description: A hearty dollop of buttery velvety mashed potato is a great place for any dish to begin. Layer on lashings of rich tomato sauce and a helping of succulent beef meatballs and you've got a dish that's satisfying, familiar, and nothing short of delicious.
